+        """
+        Thread-mode replacement for mp.context.ForkProcess on Windows.
+
+        Implements the subset of the multiprocessing.Process API that hivemind uses:
+        start, join, is_alive, terminate (no-op + warning), daemon property, pid property,
+        and name.  The ``run`` method must be overridden by subclasses.
